            "value": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22%20NLT%20NLT%20BibleText%20section%22%3E%3Csection%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%22bk_ch_vs_header%22%3EEzekiel%207%3A1-9%3A11%2C%20NLT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_7_1%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%227%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3EEzekiel%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E7%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EThe%20Coming%20of%20the%20End%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-ch-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20this%20message%20came%20to%20me%20from%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%3A%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_7_2%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%227%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BSon%20of%20man%2C%20this%20is%20what%20the%20Sovereign%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20says%20to%20Israel%3A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-sp%22%3E%26%23x201C%3BThe%20end%20is%20here!%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EWherever%20you%20look%26%23x2014%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3Eeast%2C%20west%2C%20north%2C%20or%20south%26%23x2014%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eyour%20land%20is%20finished.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_7_3%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%227%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3ENo%20hope%20remains%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Efor%20I%20will%20unleash%20my%20anger%20against%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EI%20will%20call%20you%20to%20account%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Efor%20all%20your%20detestable%20sins.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_7_4%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%227%22%20vn%3D%224%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3EI%20will%20turn%20my%20eyes%20away%20and%20show%20no%20pity.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EI%20will%20repay%20you%20for%20all%20your%20detestable%20sins.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EThen%20you%20will%20know%20that%20I%20am%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_7_5%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%227%22%20vn%3D%225%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn-sp%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E5%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BThis%20is%20what%20the%20Sovereign%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20says%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EDisaster%20after%20disaster%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eis%20coming%20your%20way!%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_7_6%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%227%22%20vn%3D%226%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E6%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20end%20has%20come.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EIt%20has%20finally%20arrived.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EYour%20final%20doom%20is%20waiting!%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_7_7%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%227%22%20vn%3D%227%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E7%3C%2Fspan%3EO%26%23xA0%3Bpeople%20of%20Israel%2C%20the%20day%20of%20your%20destruction%20is%20dawning.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EThe%20time%20has%20come%3B%20the%20day%20of%20trouble%20is%20near.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EShouts%20of%20anguish%20will%20be%20heard%20on%20the%20mountains%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Enot%20shouts%20of%20joy.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_7_8%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%227%22%20vn%3D%228%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E8%3C%2Fspan%3ESoon%20I%20will%20pour%20out%20my%20fury%20on%20you%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20unleash%20my%20anger%20against%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EI%20will%20call%20you%20to%20account%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Efor%20all%20your%20detestable%20sins.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_7_9%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%227%22%20vn%3D%229%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E9%3C%2Fspan%3EI%20will%20turn%20my%20eyes%20away%20and%20show%20no%20pity.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EI%20will%20repay%20you%20for%20all%20your%20detestable%20sins.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EThen%20you%20will%20know%20that%20it%20is%20I%2C%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ewho%20is%20striking%20the%20blow.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_7_10%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%227%22%20vn%3D%2210%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn-sp%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E10%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BThe%20day%20of%20judgment%20is%20here%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eyour%20destruction%20awaits!%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EThe%20people%26%23x2019%3Bs%20wickedness%20and%20pride%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ehave%20blossomed%20to%20full%20flower.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_7_11%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%227%22%20vn%3D%2211%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E11%3C%2Fspan%3ETheir%20violence%20has%20grown%20into%20a%20rod%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ethat%20will%20beat%20them%20for%20their%20wickedness.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3ENone%20of%20these%20proud%20and%20wicked%20people%20will%20survive.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EAll%20their%20wealth%20and%20prestige%20will%20be%20swept%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_7_12%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%227%22%20vn%3D%2212%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22